sch:rule.sch:report:
@resp and @source can
                            not be used
                            together

@resp or @source is
                            expected for
                            div[@type='translation']

sch:rule.sch:assert:
Gap with the attribute
                            @unit="component" can only be used inside seg with the
                            @type="component".

The element gap with
                            @quantity and @unit="line" expect either the use of @precision="low" or
                            the element certainty.

Space can't have @quantity and @unit attributes with
                            @type='binding-hole' or @type='descender' or @type='ascender', the only
                            @type possible is @type='defect'.

@type='ref' can only be
                            used inside the translation part of the
                            edition

sch:rule.sch:report:
@n is
                            mandatory with
                            milestone/@type="ref"
